#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:1 of
msgid "Return the Discrete Fourier Transform sample frequencies."
msgstr "返回离散傅里叶变换的采样频率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:3 of
msgid ""
"The returned float tensor `f` contains the frequency bin centers in "
"cycles per unit of the sample spacing (with zero at the start).  For "
"instance, if the sample spacing is in seconds, then the frequency unit is"
" cycles/second."
msgstr ""
"返回的浮点张量 `f` 包含以采样间隔单位为周期的频率箱中心（起始为零）。例如"
"，如果采样间隔是以秒为单位，则频率单位为周期/秒。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:7 of
msgid "Given a window length `n` and a sample spacing `d`::"
msgstr "给定窗口长度 `n` 和采样间隔 `d`：："

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:12 of
msgid "Window length."
msgstr "窗口长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:14 of
msgid "Sample spacing (inverse of the sampling rate). Defaults to 1."
msgstr "采样间隔（采样率的倒数）。默认为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:16 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:18 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:21 of
msgid "**f** -- Array of length `n` containing the sample frequencies."
msgstr "**f** -- 包含采样频率的长度为 `n` 的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftfreq.fftfreq:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

